title: ELEMENT 'RISE & SHINE' NYJAH HUSTON VIDEO - OFFICIAL TRAILER - SKATEBOARDING
description:
Nyjah Huston and Element formed a relationship when Nyjah was only 7-years old. Then, a twig on the Element tree, Nyjah grew into his own... In 2011 Nyjah 3-peat'd at Street League, and won X-Games gold, but he's out now to prove his talents where their matter most; in the streets.

Element presents "RISE & SHINE" - The Nyjah Huston video, available on iTunes worldwide on 11.11.11.
Music by:
Loren Humphrey
